com.paypal.selion.internal.reports.model

Class BaseLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.internal.reports.model.BaseLog

  • public class BaseLog
extends Object
    This class serves as the base for all logging with respect to UI operations being done either on the browser or on a native app in a simulator/device. Any functionality that intends to provide a reporting capability similar to SeLionReporter should leverage this class for the basic functionalities and add up only customizations as and where required. This is an internal class for use in Selion and clients of SeLion should have no need for referencing this public class.
